OL,3,CPoliticians risk 'destabilising'
OL,4,Chealth sector if St Pier not suspended
OL,6,FGuernsey's health sector is "at risk
OL,7,Fof destabilisation" if politicians do
OL,8,Fnot suspend Deputy Chief Minister
OL,9,FGavin St Pier, the British Medical
OL,10,FAssociation (BMA) has warned.
OL,12,FThe States' independent Commissioner
OL,13,Ffor Standards, Dr Melissa McCullough,
OL,14,Fhas recommended that Deputy St Pier
OL,15,Fshould be suspended from the Assembly
OL,16,Ffor 25 days without pay, with a vote
OL,17,Fscheduled for Wednesday 26 November.
