OL,3,CPoliticians risk 'destabilising'
OL,4,Chealth sector if St Pier not suspended
OL,6,FThe Chair of the Medical Specialist
OL,7,FGroup, which employs Dr Bohin,
OL,8,Fbelieves the Deputy Chief Minister
OL,9,Fmust be sanctioned for "the long and
OL,10,Funfair campaign waged against Dr
OL,11,FBohin".
OL,13,FDr Steve Evans adds: "The key finding
OL,14,Fby the Commissioner is that Deputy St
OL,15,FPier confirmed "confidential and
OL,16,Fseriously inaccurate and misleading
OL,17,Finformation" in a call with a Guardian
OL,18,Fjournalist."
