OL,3,CPoliticians risk 'destabilising'
OL,4,Chealth sector if St Pier not suspended
OL,6,FDr Evans argues this caused "deep
OL,7,Fharm" to Dr Bohin, the paediatric
OL,8,Fservice and public trust.
OL,10,FThe BMA has urged politicians to
OL,11,Fconsider the impact their decision
OL,12,Fwill have on the island's medical
OL,13,Fcommunity.
OL,15,FThey said: "Not suspending him would
OL,16,Fbe a significant blow, and we would
OL,17,Fquestion the support we have from our
OL,18,FStates Members.
OL,20,F"The entire medical sector could be at
OL,21,Frisk of destabilisation as a result.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G4/9
