OL,3,CPoliticians risk 'destabilising'
OL,4,Chealth sector if St Pier not suspended
OL,6,F"It would be a real problem for
OL,7,Frecruitment, retention and morale."
OL,9,FDeputy St Pier named Dr Bohin under
OL,10,Fparliamentary privilege during a
OL,11,Fspeech to the Assembly about
OL,12,Fsafeguarding in 2022.
OL,14,FHe received four Code of Conduct
OL,15,Fcomplaints, leading to a formal
OL,16,Freprimand.
OL,18,FHowever, Deputy St Pier was not found
OL,19,Fto have abused his parliamentary
OL,20,Fprivilege, following a complaint from
OL,21,Fthe Health and Social Care Committee.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G5/9
