OL,3,CPoliticians risk 'destabilising'
OL,4,Chealth sector if St Pier not suspended
OL,6,FThe Deputy Chief Minister claims he
OL,7,Fwas trying to advocate for 27 families
OL,8,Fwith safeguarding concerns about
OL,9,FGuernsey's medical sector and that the
OL,10,Fisland's Medical Specialist Group
OL,11,Fdeclined to meet with him about these
OL,12,Fissues.
OL,14,FHowever, the BMA still believe this
OL,15,Fwas not a sufficient reason to justify
OL,16,Fhis actions regarding naming Dr Bohin.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G7/9
