OL,3,CPoliticians risk 'destabilising'
OL,4,Chealth sector if St Pier not suspended
OL,6,FMat Dorrien, a Guernsey BMA
OL,7,Fspokesperson, adds: "Our members are
OL,8,Fextremely concerned about a local
OL,9,Fdoctor being attacked in the States of
OL,10,FGuernsey, despite being exonerated by
OL,11,Fa robust governor's procedure.
OL,13,F"Doctors expect to be held to account
OL,14,Ffor their actions and have got robust
OL,15,Fgovernance procedures and regulatory
OL,16,Fbodies to make sure this happens.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G8/9
