OL,6,F"For a doctor to be personally named
OL,7,Fand attacked in the States of Guernsey
OL,8,For the Houses of Parliament, feels
OL,9,Fentirely disproportionate and unfair,
OL,10,Fespecially as they have no right of
OL,11,Freply in that environment because
OL,12,Fthey're bound by confidentiality."
